query:
SELECT a.*, e.tipoEvento, e.dataEvento, f.nome as formandoNome 
FROM agendamentos a 
INNER JOIN eventos e ON a.eventoId = e.id 
INNER JOIN formandos f ON a.formandoId = f.id 
WHERE e.turmaId = (SELECT id FROM turmas WHERE codigo = '553') 
LIMIT 10
